data.description: Exceptional residence situated in Plantation, boasting 4 bedrooms, a versatile Game Room/Office, and 2 bathrooms. The open concept design integrates a spacious kitchen, family room, and dining area. Featuring impact windows, new appliances, a recently replaced roof, seamless gutters, and a pool enclosure overlooking a serene canal. Indulge in year-round swimming in a pool that includes automatic water heating and chilling. The interior has brand-new laminate wood floors, ceiling fans in every room, and a convenient 2-car garage. Outside, the expansive grounds with fruit trees and a state-of-the-art irrigation system.  Prime location, within walking distance of all school levels, shopping malls, and plazas. This residence offers an Equal Housing Opportunity.
